			<h3 class="first"><a href="#p8">Patch 4.0.1 live</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=8#p8"><img src="./styles/thedruidsgrove/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2" style="color: #AA0000;" class="username-coloured">Yrys</a></strong> &raquo; Thu Oct 14, 2010 1:54 am </p>

			

			<div class="content">World of Warcraft patch 4.0.1 is live as of Tuesday; this is the Cataclysm preparation patch that includes things like major class changes and talent revamps, pre-Cataclysm zone events, and user interface changes, among many others.<br /><br />Read on for the full patch notes...</div>

			

		</div>

		
